msgid "Tools for building images and managing containers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: containers-build-tools.xml:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "This chapter provides a brief overview of tools for building images and managing containers. Most of the tools mentioned below are part of the <emphasis role=\"strong\">&sls; &productnumber; Containers Module</emphasis> . You can see the full list of packages in the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Containers Module</emphasis> in the <link xlink:href=\"https://scc.suse.com/packages?name=SUSE%20Linux%20Enterprise%20Server&amp;version=&productnumber-regurl;&amp;arch=x86_64&amp;query=&amp;module=1963\">&scc;</link> ."
msgstr ""

